ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#206: FILE: sound/drivers/serial-u16550.c:793:
+	if ((uart = kcalloc(sizeof(*uart), GFP_KERNEL)) == NULL)

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

